==English==

===Etymology===
Apparently from the resemblence of the tree to Joshua holding out his spear (Joshua 8:18: ‘And the LORD said unto Joshua, stretch out the spear that is in thy hand toward Ai; for I will give it into thine hand. And Joshua stretched out the spear that he had in his hand toward the city.’  KJV).

===Noun===
'''[[w:Joshua|Joshua]] [[tree]]'''

# A [[yucca]], ''[[Yucca brevifolia]]'', of the southwestern U.S. with spiky leaves.

